- Correct display some rectangle in cLCARSNGDisplayMenu::DrawFrameDisplay
- Optimizing displaymenu to avoid flickering
- Refactor DrawDisk()
- Prevent "Rec:" from flickering in displaychannel.c

Version 0.3.2
